	CALL SINGLE_DRAWLINE
	PRINTFORM 所属武将:
	PRINTFORM %ANAME(GET_COUNTRY_BOSS(SELECTED))%  
	FOR LOCAL, 0, CHARANUM
		SIF CFLAG:(LOCAL):所属 == SELECTED && LOCAL != GET_COUNTRY_BOSS(SELECTED)
			PRINTFORM %ANAME(LOCAL)%  
	NEXT
	PRINTL
	PRINTFORM 捕虜:
